Event Master Name: Verify epic LT-73558 Part 1 with 1k event master - 1
Description:
🎉 GRAND OPENING EVENT – SUMMER FEST 2025 🎉
🌟 A Spectacular Celebration Awaits! 🌟
👉 Date: Saturday, July 12, 2025
 👉 Time: 4:00 PM – 10:00 PM
 👉 Location: Central Park, New York City
📌 Event Highlights:
🎶 Live Performances from top artists
 🍔 Food & Beverage Stalls featuring cuisines from around the world
 🎡 Exciting Carnival Rides for all ages
 🎆 Grand Fireworks Show at 9:30 PM
🔹 Schedule of Activities:
1. Opening Ceremony (4:00 PM - 5:00 PM)
🎤 Welcome speech by the Mayor

🎭 Cultural Performances

2. Main Attractions (5:00 PM - 9:30 PM)
A. Music Concert (Main Stage) 🎸
 B. Food Court Experience 🍕
 C. Art & Craft Fair 🎨
3. Grand Finale – Fireworks Show (9:30 PM - 10:00 PM) 🎆
💡 Why You Should Attend?
✔ Unforgettable entertainment
 ✔ Free entry & giveaways
 ✔ A chance to meet celebrities
 ✔ Fun for all ages!
🔔 Important Notes:
❗ Limited parking available – use public transport 🚋
 ❗ No outside food & drinks allowed 🚫
 ❗ Bring your ID for age-restricted zones 🆔
🎟️ How to Register?
➡ Visit our website: www.summerfest2025.com
 ➡ Call us at: (123) 456-7890
📢 Follow us on social media for updates!
 📷 Instagram: @summerfest2025
 📘 Facebook: fb.com/summerfest2025
 🐦 Twitter: @summerfest2025
🌟 SEE YOU THERE! 🌟

🎉 GRAND OPENING EVENT – SUMMER FEST 2025 🎉
🌟 A Spectacular Celebration Awaits! 🌟
👉 Date: Saturday, July 12, 2025
 👉 Time: 4:00 PM – 10:00 PM
 👉 Location: Central Park, New York City
📌 Event Highlights:
🎶 Live Performances from top artists
 🍔 Food & Beverage Stalls featuring cuisines from around the world
 🎡 Exciting Carnival Rides for all ages
 🎆 Grand Fireworks Show at 9:30 PM
🔹 Schedule of Activities:
1. Opening Ceremony (4:00 PM - 5:00 PM)
🎤 Welcome speech by the Mayor

🎭 Cultural Performances

2. Main Attractions (5:00 PM - 9:30 PM)
A. Music Concert (Main Stage) 🎸
 B. Food Court Experience 🍕
 C. Art & Craft Fair 🎨
3. Grand Finale – Fireworks Show (9:30 PM - 10:00 PM) 🎆
💡 Why You Should Attend?
✔ Unforgettable entertainment
 ✔ Free entry & giveaways
 ✔ A chance to meet celebrities
 ✔ Fun for all ages!
🔔 Important Notes:
❗ Limited parking available – use public transport 🚋
 ❗ No outside food & drinks allowed 🚫
 ❗ Bring your ID for age-restricted zones 🆔
🎟️ How to Register?
➡ Visit our website: www.summerfest2025.com
 ➡ Call us at: (123) 456-7890
📢 Follow us on social media for updates!
 📷 Instagram: @summerfest2025
 📘 Facebook: fb.com/summerfest2025
 🐦 Twitter: @summerfest2025
🌟 SEE YOU THERE! 🌟
